room_title: Escape room "Hospital Room 151" by Clue Quest in Oklahoma City
review: Been in Clara's Diary (unsuccessful) and Room 151 (successful). Both times just as fun, and the staff was genuinely excited when we escaped. Definitely need to try the other rooms!
